9
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,620
-Give me 20 seconds.
-Alert Captain Robau

10
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:36,590
that Starfleet advises your ship
to proceed with caution.

11
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,200
Polarise the viewscreen.

12
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,670
Could whatever this is
be of Klingon origin?

13
