I'm unfamiliar with Ambassador Spock.

52
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,390
-What is the current stardate?
-Stardate?

53
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:13,010
Twenty-two thirty-three zero-four.

54
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,510
Where are you from?

55
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,460
Sir, they're locked on our signal.
They're launching again!

56
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,060
Bravo-six manoeuvre! Fire full spread!

57
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:39,430
-Seventeen more out!
-I'm initiating General Order 13!

58
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,350
-We're evacuating!
-Yes, sir!

59
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:49,360
All decks, this is the Captain speaking.
Evacuate the ship immediately.

60
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,489
Get to your designated shuttlecraft.
Repeat. Evacuate...

61
