Move! This one's closed!
Let's go! Get him up!

64
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,570
I'm on my way!

65
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,790
-George.
-You're okay. Thank God.

66
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:11,609
